          { "term": "Ho … anni", "translation": "I am … years old", "example": "Ho 25 anni." },
          { "term": "Mi piace…", "translation": "I like…", "example": "Mi piace il calcio." },
          { "term": "Abito a…", "translation": "I live in…", "example": "Abito a Milano." }
        ]},
        { "id": "grammar-01", "type": "text", "content": "**Key verbs:**\n- *essere*: io **sono**, tu **sei**, lui/lei **è**\n- *avere*: io **ho**, tu **hai**, lui/lei **ha**\n\n**Structures:**\n- *Sono di* + city/country (origin)\n- *Ho* + number + *anni* (age)\n- *Mi piace* + noun (likes)" }
      ]
    },
    {
